```plantuml
@startuml odh-labs_predictive-maint

actor User

participant "Web Application" as WebApp
participant "Kafka" as Kafka
participant "Consumer Application" as Consumer
participant "Seldon Core" as Seldon
participant "MinIO" as MinIO
participant "OpenShift" as OpenShift

User -> WebApp : Capture image
WebApp -> Kafka : Send image
Kafka -> Consumer : Stream image
Consumer -> Seldon : Perform inference
Seldon -> Consumer : Return prediction
Consumer -> MinIO : Store results
MinIO -> WebApp : Update dashboard

User -> OpenShift : Deploy model
OpenShift -> Seldon : Deploy and expose model

@enduml
```